data.description: Classic Emerywood home with beautiful all brick exterior and welcoming front porch. One of the largest lots on the street with fenced in backyard and large deck for entertaining. All main level living with hardwood floors throughout. Recently updated kitchen. Finished basement offers additional living space and great storage. This home is move-in ready.
